latestIgtvVideos.title: Curly to straight using the spectrum infrared duo
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
If you’re in need of a good styling iron and blow dryer this is what you need The Spectrum infrared duo from Eva Nyc @evahairnyc available at @ultabeauty 
I love my results 😍
This duo has in infrared beam that penetrated deep in to the hair heating hair from the inside out and locks in moisture to boost your hairs natural gloss ✨
The blow dryer is very lightweight and it has 2 speeds and 3 heat setting. It has an ion technology for faster drying and minimizes frizz ( I set mine to medium heat )
The styling iron has a 1 hr auto shut off for safe styling 😌 
I also used @evanyc Mane Magic 10 in 1 primer for gloss and thermal protection ( it smells so good )

latestIgtvVideos.title: Get ready w me 🔮 deep conditioning and wet plopping
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
#pressplay 🔮 ( i took 30 mins on this caption so please read 👇🏽 ) 
Deep conditioning is just so satisfying! 
I’m using @curlganix Hydration and repair butter masque it’s so buttery and thick how I like my hair masks and left my hair soft of course 💦 ( use code BRI10 for $$ off) ( left in 15 mins and rinsed out but not completely ) bc these split ends need to go! I know my hair appears very healthy but I still have old bleached ends and my hair takes way too long to grow out no matter how much I trim and take care of my hair but it’s slowly getting healthier ! 
To style : 
Used @curlganix Hydrating Delight cream  w @floracurl defining gel 💦 and then I used a shower or color cap to wet plop for about 30 mins and once again my results were amazing! ( I’ve been trying wet plopping because I struggle with getting definition at the roots and this method seems to help with that) 
When I took the cap off my hair was still very wet so I diffused on low heat and cool air once it was almost fully dry. And bam! you see these results ?!
Makeup :
Foundation - @lancomeofficial teint idol shade 390
Eyes- @wetnwildbeauty + @bretmanrock Jungle Rock collection palette ( these colors are beautiful and very pigmented)
Also added @hiddenjewellcosmetics 
Glitter 🥂 .
